cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper discusses a deep learning approach for automated segmentation of cardiac MRI images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of neural networks for segmentation also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could be classified under multimedia (cs.MM).
